 17/3/18 Red Lodg Another fine day and thing are not too bad at all for the troop . The Band was play here all the morn and went down to the Catacomb in the afternoon . Colonel Jame call in for a yarn be much buck up by his leav . Afternoon walk to the Catacomb . Wonder tunnel and drive all underground , electr light and fit with bunk . Just like a Troop-deck . As one chap say "you onli want to put a propel on now and turn her head to home " Dr Simmond leav us for the Field Ambulanc McMahon now reign in his stead . The war seem far away tonight as we sat in our open air mess yarn . Habel , the mess Corpl was hit tonight slight on the hand
